OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,FOlly Murs has opened up about how
OL,8,Ffatherhood has shifted his perspective
OL,9,Fas he prepares to take on a
OL,10,F"petrifying" endurance challenge for
OL,11,FSoccer Aid's 20th anniversary.
OL,13,FThe 41-year-old singer will take on
OL,14,Fhis Into The Unknown challenge to
OL,15,Fraise money for Unicef next month `
OL,16,Fduring which he will run, cycle and
OL,17,Frow 400km across the UK until he
OL,18,Freaches London Stadium in Stratford.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@LO]
