PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1777464667
OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,FThe singer is a keen advocate who has
OL,8,Fbeen involved with Unicef for more
OL,9,Fthan a decade, and told described how
OL,10,Fbecoming a parent has shifted his
OL,11,Fmindset towards his fundraising
OL,12,Fefforts.
OL,14,FMurs said: "As a parent myself, you
OL,15,Fkind of put yourself in (other
OL,16,Fpeople's) shoes, don't you?"
OL,26,@vD@LOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
