OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1777464667
OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,FReflecting on a recent trip to Romania
OL,8,Fto see Unicef's work in action, the
OL,9,Ffather-of-two said: "When you do trips
OL,10,Flike this, it just puts things into
OL,11,Fperspective of how lucky we live our
OL,12,Flives in the UK, and how we don't live
OL,13,Fin a war.
OL,15,F"Currently, we don't have those fears.
OL,16,FAt the moment, I'm going through quite
OL,17,Fa lot with the kids, but all I'm
OL,18,Fhaving to do is the basic stuff that
OL,19,Fwe do as parents: keeping them alive
OL,20,Fevery day, feeding them, nurturing
OL,21,Fthem, supporting them, loving them."
OL,26,@qD@UOUwD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
