CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1777464667
OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,FReferring to the ongoing conflict in
OL,8,FUkraine following Russia's full-scale
OL,9,Finvasion in 2022, Murs added: "If I
OL,10,Fwas in Ukraine now where you're having
OL,11,Fto make big decisions on where you
OL,12,Flive, and there's a war, and I don't
OL,13,Fknow from each day if I'm going to be
OL,14,Fsafe
OL,16,F"It definitely puts things into
OL,17,Fperspective."
OL,26,@qD@_OUxD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
