PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1777464667
OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,FThe chart-topping pop star also
OL,8,Fadmitted he is "pretty scared" for the
OL,9,Fchallenge as he does not know where it
OL,10,Fwill take him, with the route to be
OL,11,Frevealed only moments before he sets
OL,12,Foff from Manchester's Old Trafford
OL,13,Fstadium.
OL,15,FHe said: "This challenge was an
OL,16,Fopportunity for me to do something
OL,17,Famazing, something different, and
OL,18,Fleave something behind with Soccer Aid.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@^O]wD@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1777464667
OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,F"It's going to be something that
OL,8,Fhopefully will be something people can
OL,9,Flook back on and go, 'wow, Olly raised
OL,10,Fthis much money, and we did something
OL,11,Fspecial' ` and it's something to show
OL,12,Fmy kids when they get older."
OL,14,FMurs recounted the intensive training
OL,15,Fhe has undergone to prepare for the
OL,16,Fendurance task, and said: "I've
OL,17,Fperformed and I've sung, I do that for
OL,18,Fa living. Doing something at this
OL,19,Flevel of fitness, I've had to train
OL,20,Flike a pro athlete ` and I'm
OL,21,Fdefinitely not a pro athlete.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@]O]xD@[OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1777464667
OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,F"I'm petrified about it, but I've
OL,8,Flearned the techniques now, and I'm
OL,9,Fjust gonna have to just battle through
OL,10,Fmy own head and get to the end.
OL,12,F"I'm just gonna have to go with this
OL,13,Fand take each day as it comes... It's
OL,14,Fmadness, it wasn't on my bingo card to
OL,15,Fbe doing it this year."
OL,17,FMurs added: "There's people out there
OL,18,Fin the world that you know are living
OL,19,Fon edge and living afraid, and all
OL,20,Fthey want to do is get their kids safe.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@WO]yD@MOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
