PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1777464667
OL,3,COlly Murs reflects on fatherhood as he
OL,4,Cprepares for 'petrifying' Soccer Aid
OL,5,Ctask
OL,7,F"We're lucky and fortunate in the UK
OL,8,Fto be able to do that every single day
OL,9,Fand live in a comfortable space."
OL,11,FMurs will set off on his challenge on
OL,12,FMay 11, and will share updates with
OL,13,Fhis fans and supporters across the
OL,14,Fweek as he tackles cross-country
OL,15,Fterrain, winding roads and stretches
OL,16,Fof open water.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@aO]
